snippet.title: The Cursed Legacy [Official trailer] - PC
snippet.description:
✔ https://store.steampowered.com/app/2824210/The_Cursed_Legacy/

The Cursed Legacy is a supernatural investigation set in a dark and mysterious atmosphere. Keep calm and solve the riddles to unravel this strange disappearance. But be careful, you're not alone!
